 4. the person playing canasta is between the dancer and the electrician##2
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person playing canasta##8
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the software-developer##1
10. the electrician is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
12. the dancer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
14. the electrician is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
