The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, taxi, train, trike
 1. the owner of the goldfish is not the person eating pepper##6
 2. the owner of the dog is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the person driving the taxi##7
 3. the person drinking lemonade is the person eating kale##1
 4. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
 5. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the train and the person eating pumpkin##2
 6. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 7. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating kale##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
 9. the person driving the taxi is not the owner of the goldfish##6
10. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking juice is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
12. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
14. the person eating corn is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |    3     |   4    |
