.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, milk, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, electrician, musician, police-officer
There are 4 different nationalities: british, canadian, argentine, american
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, subway, van
 1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 2. the american is not to the right of the electrician##8
 3. the british is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the american##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
 6. the person driving the van is the person drinking juice##1
 7. the police-officer is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 8. the musician is on the far right##1
 9. the electrician is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
11. the british is somewhere to the left of the american##5
12. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the canadian##5
13. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the police-officer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | juice          | iced-tea | milk        | sprite    |
| Job         | police-officer | doctor   | electrician | musician  |
| Nationality         | argentine           | british     | american       | canadian  |
| Transport   | van            | subway   | scooter     | quad-bike |

