.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, singing, sudoku
There 4 different types of food: lime, garlic, asparagus, broccoli
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, romance, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, jazz, reggae
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person eating lime##8
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 4. the person eating broccoli is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person eating asparagus##6
 6. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the person eating asparagus##8
 8. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person eating asparagus and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku    | singing   | board-games   | collecting |
| Food           | lime | garlic    | asparagus | broccoli    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | adventure | animation     | western    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | jazz      | indie         | reggae     |

 